Navigation pane components should show the full heirarchy from graph

In the navigation for the component editor, the components view is flat. It should be an expanding tree; the hierarchy is a DAG. You can grab the DAG with the graph API.

It should start at the launchables, but from there, I should be able to expand into subcomponents. 

Ideally, we'd use the same control as in the files navigation view, but starting closed instead of open.

----------
Can you create a <List> block? It should have the following syntax:

<List id="graphicOrganizerArguments" items=3 minItems=1 maxItems=10>
  <Argument/>
</List>

And this should render as:

<>
<Argument id="graphicOrganizerArguments_1"/>
<Argument id="graphicOrganizerArguments_2"/>
<Argument id="graphicOrganizerArguments_3"/>
[+] [-]
</>

Where the plus and minus add and remove arguments.
