In the preview view, can you move debug to go from being managed in the URL (debug=true) to being managed by redux? Notice redux gives helpers for managing settings. Ideally, we'd have a debug toggle on top of the page as a control if we're logged in as a developer (which is 100% of the time right now, but it will go away once we have accounts).
