Can you please holistically change the term for the block definition from 'Spec' to 'Blueprint'?

After that, can you holistically refactor all of the blocks to have:

1) A blueprint file (Block.js), ending with a .js or .ts extension
2) A component file (_Block.jsx), ending with a .jsx or .tsx extension, with the React component?

Right now, a few are still in the old format of one file.

Please be sure to update the documentation as well.

